									<h5 id="subject_147931">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/(jul-2016)-story-generator/(jul-2016)-story-generator-submission-thread/msg147931/#msg147931" rel="nofollow">Re: [Jul 2016] - Story Generator - Submission Thread</a>
