									<h5 id="subject_148576">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/(jul-2016)-story-generator/(jul-2016)-story-generator-submission-thread/msg148576/#msg148576" rel="nofollow">Re: [Jul 2016] - Story Generator - Submission Thread</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>Reply #6 on:</strong> July 24, 2016, 11:02:54 PM &#187;</div>
									<div id="msg_148576_quick_mod"></div>
