						<div class="poster">
							<h4>
								<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/profile/?u=40227" title="View the profile of Mr.J">Mr.J</a>
							</h4>
							<ul class="reset smalltext" id="msg_148971_extra_info">
								<li class="title">Anus Dracula formerly known as Arse Demon and Writing Contest Regular</li>
