									<h5 id="subject_148995">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/(jul-2016)-story-generator/(jul-2016)-story-generator-submission-thread/msg148995/#msg148995" rel="nofollow">Re: [Jul 2016] - Story Generator - Submission Thread</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>Reply #10 on:</strong> August 01, 2016, 07:24:41 AM &#187;</div>
