									<h5 id="subject_149017">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/(jul-2016)-story-generator/(jul-2016)-story-generator-submission-thread/msg149017/#msg149017" rel="nofollow">Re: [Jul 2016] - Story Generator - Submission Thread</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>Reply #11 on:</strong> August 01, 2016, 01:14:27 PM &#187;</div>
